descript.abstract: This dataset displays the point location of the top ten sites where stormwater is discharged into the Southern California Bight. The data was summarized by Eric Steine (Southern California Coastal Water Research Project) in November 2008. Eric Steine used the following reference: Ackerman, D. and Schiff, K. 2003. Modeling storm water mass emissions to the Southern California Bight. Journal of Environmental Engineering 129 (4): 308-317.
descript.purpose: To display the location of the top ten sites where stormwater is discharged into the Southern California Bight.
